     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PYM     8
     C                     PARM           PBN     2
      *   MEISAI  FOR KEY
     C           KEY       KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KSAHZ   80
     C                     KFLD           KSARD   20
      *   ROLL-UP FOR KEY
     C           KEY1      KLIST
