     C                     KFLD           WSARD   20
     C                     KFLD           WNONU   40
     C                     KFLD           WKOJO   1
     C                     KFLD           WUKEI   4
      *   ROLL-DOWN FOR KEY
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           WSAHZB  80
     C                     KFLD           WSARDB  20
     C                     KFLD           WNONUB  40
     C                     KFLD           WKOJOB  1
