      ******************
      ***  KEY ﾉ ﾈｮmb  ***
     C                     Z-ADDWYM,IX    ODAY
     C                     Z-ADDWBN,IX    OBIN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WNY
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WHF
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WNM
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WKJ
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    WUK
     C                     Z-ADD0         WCK
     C                     Z-ADDWYM,IX    KSAHZ
